{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441320/extras/title.png?t=1738163409\" />Get ready to dive into the ultra-dynamic universe of <i>Hyperdrive Horizon</i>, an electrifying space racing game where speed, reflexes, and adrenaline are the keys to victory!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Modes</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Single player:</strong> Challenge yourself to beat your own records and improve with every race.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>VS AI:</strong> Test your skills against highly competitive AI opponents designed to push you to your limits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441320/extras/gif.gif?t=1738163409\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Ships and Customization</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlockable Ships:</strong> Earn new  ships with unique designs as you race.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customizable Colors:</strong> Make your ship your own by choosing from a variety of vibrant color schemes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441320/extras/gif1.gif?t=1738163409\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Boosts and barrel rolls:</strong> Use boosts to speed past your opponents and barrel rolls to skillfully dodge obstacles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Procedurally generated tracks:</strong> Every race is unique, offering fresh and unpredictable challenges with dynamically generated terrain.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Global Leaderboard:</strong> Compare your best times and achievements with players from around the world to see who is the fastest racer.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Race across a vast lunar canyon, dodge obstacles at high speed, and collect boosts to push yourself even further. With fluid gameplay and increasing difficulty, <strong><i>Hyperdrive Horizon</i></strong> offers a tough challenge for players seeking fast-paced action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Are you up for the challenge?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play <strong><i>Hyperdrive Horizon</i></strong> and experience a game that combines the simple with the extreme!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Flight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3441320/223076f0405ba1440583ce05a73af362b5490b5c.jpg"},{"name":"New Challenger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3441320/a2ed1567789f6d94bd03f2dc47c7c2da3212828a.jpg"},{"name":"Circuit Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3441320/d71cdc876d558b085f63c56a017adc8352216d47.jpg"},{"name":"Rival Vanquisher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3441320/8cf83b7a7b4fb2182def75c28415d49a6f46ae23.jpg"},{"name":"Untouchable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3441320/de3d336859ff1fdc9bd9f47542e1ac1774dbf588.jpg"},{"name":"Barrel Roll Prodigy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3441320/6b3030682c6b68e4ea946232b0bd0b670ee406e3.jpg"},{"name":"Barrel Roll Enthusiast","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3441320/7f633dbe2962b5d4a891d2a69daea8cd4c0f84fe.jpg"},{"name":"Barrel Roll Fanatic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3441320/f